---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout title="À propos - Manolia Kocaoglu">
  <Header currentPage="apropos" />

  <!-- Background elements -->
  <div class="grid-bg"></div>
  <div class="pixel-decorations">
    <div class="pixel-shape" style="top: 15%; left: 8%;"></div>
    <div class="pixel-shape" style="top: 25%; right: 12%;"></div>
    <div class="pixel-cross" style="top: 45%; left: 5%;"></div>
    <div class="pixel-cross" style="bottom: 30%; right: 8%;"></div>
    <div class="pixel-plus" style="top: 60%; right: 15%;"></div>
    <div class="pixel-plus" style="bottom: 20%; left: 10%;"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-content">
      <!-- Carte joueur avec avatar -->
      <div class="player-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="pixel-corners"></div>
          <h2>JOUEUR: <br> <br>MANOLIA KOCAOGLU</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="avatar-section">
            <div class="avatar-frame">
              <img src="/manolia.svg" alt="Manolia" />
            </div>
            <div class="level-badge">
              <span class="level-text">LEVEL</span>
              <br>
              <span class="level-number">20</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="stats-section">
            <div class="stat-group">
              <span class="stat-label">Classe:</span>
              <span class="stat-value">Designer créatif</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-group">
              <span class="stat-label">Niveau:</span>
              <span class="stat-value">Étudiante en MMI</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-group">
              <span class="stat-label">Spécialité:</span>
              <span class="stat-value">Création UI/UX</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Compétences (barres de stats) -->
      <div class="skills-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h2>COMPÉTENCES</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="skill">
            <div class="skill-info">
              <span class="skill-name">Créativité</span>
              <span class="skill-stars">★★★★★</span>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-bar">
              <div class="skill-fill" style="width: 100%;"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="skill">
            <div class="skill-info">
              <span class="skill-name">Imagination</span>
              <span class="skill-stars">★★★★</span>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-bar">
              <div class="skill-fill" style="width: 80%;"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="skill">
            <div class="skill-info">
              <span class="skill-name">Curiosité</span>
              <span class="skill-stars">★★★★★</span>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-bar">
              <div class="skill-fill" style="width: 100%;"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="skill">
            <div class="skill-info">
              <span class="skill-name">Esprit d'équipe</span>
              <span class="skill-stars">★★★★</span>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-bar">
              <div class="skill-fill" style="width: 80%;"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio / Description -->
      <div class="bio-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h2>BIO</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="bio-text">
            Passionnée par la création visuelle et numérique. J'aime donner vie à des identités graphiques et des interfaces qui racontent une histoire. Mon parcours en MMI spécialité Création m'a permis d'explorer l'UI/UX, l'identité visuelle et la direction artistique à travers des projets scolaires et personnels.
          </p>
          <p class="bio-text">
            Curieuse et imaginative, je considère chaque projet comme une nouvelle aventure où je peux expérimenter, apprendre et inventer des univers créatifs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-footer">
          <a href="/cv.pdf" download class="action-button">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
              <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4M7 10l5 5 5-5M12 15V3" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Télécharger mon CV</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="action-button secondary">
            <span>Contact</span>
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
              <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  :global(body) {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .grid-bg {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: 
      linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 50px 50px;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .pixel-decorations {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .pixel-shape,
  .pixel-cross,
  .pixel-plus {
    position: absolute;
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .pixel-cross {
    background: 
      linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 6px, transparent 6px, transparent 12px, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 12px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 6px, transparent 6px, transparent 12px, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 12px);
    animation-delay: 1s;
  }

  .pixel-plus {
    clip-path: polygon(40% 0%, 60% 0%, 60% 40%, 100% 40%, 100% 60%, 60% 60%, 60% 100%, 40% 100%, 40% 60%, 0% 60%, 0% 40%, 40% 40%);
    animation-delay: 2s;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.7; }
    50% { transform: translateY(-12px); opacity: 1; }
  }

  .about-container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: 100vw;
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 140px 40px 40px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 1300px;
    width: 100%;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    max-height: calc(100vh - 180px);
  }

  /* Cards communes */
  .player-card,
  .skills-card,
  .bio-card {
    background: #111b9f;
    border: 4px solid #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    position: relative;
    animation: cardAppear 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes cardAppear {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .card-header {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    border-bottom: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    padding: 10px 16px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .card-header h2 {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #ffffff;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .card-body {
    padding: 14px;
  }

  /* Player Card */
  .player-card {
    grid-row: 1 / 3;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .avatar-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .avatar-frame {
    width: 110px;
    height: 110px;
    border: 3px solid #ffffff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px #111b9f, 4px 4px 0 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .avatar-frame img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transform: scale(1.4);
  }

  .level-badge {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    background: #ffd700;
    border: 2px solid #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 3px 3px 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .level-text {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 0.4rem;
    color: #1a237e;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .level-number {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #1a237e;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .stats-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .stat-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    color: #6b7fff;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #ffffff;
    line-height: 1.6;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  /* Skills Card */
  .skills-card {
    animation-delay: 0.1s;
  }

  .skill {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .skill:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .skill-info {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .skill-name {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .skill-stars {
    color: #ffd700;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .skill-bar {
    height: 16px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .skill-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6b7fff 0%, #ffd700 100%);
    animation: fillBar 1s ease-out;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .skill-fill::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: -100%;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.4), transparent);
    animation: shimmer 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes fillBar {
    from { width: 0; }
  }

  @keyframes shimmer {
    to { left: 100%; }
  }

  /* Bio Card */
  .bio-card {
    animation-delay: 0.2s;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .bio-text {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #f5f5ff;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .bio-text:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .card-footer {
    margin-top: auto;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border-top: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .action-button {
    flex: 1;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 5px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #111b9f;
    border: 3px solid #ffffff;
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 0.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 3px 3px 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .action-button:hover {
    transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
    box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .action-button.secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .action-button.secondary:hover {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #111b9f;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto auto auto;
      overflow-y: auto;
      height: auto;
    }

    .player-card {
      grid-row: auto;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-container {
      padding: 120px 20px 40px;
    }

    .avatar-frame {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
    }

    .card-body {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .card-footer {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .action-button {
      font-size: 0.6rem;
    }
  }
</style>